*Veče* je bilo tiho i mirno. (The evening was quiet and peaceful.)
*Večeras* ćemo gledati film. (We will watch a movie tonight.)
Nakon *večere* smo otišli na šetnju. (After dinner we went for a walk.)
Kod nas se *večeri* obično rano. (We usually eat dinner early.)
*Večeras* ćemo se družiti sa prijateljima. (Tonight we are going to hang out with friends.)